{"word":"καθέζομαι","slug":"καθέζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καθέζομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>:— <i>to sit down, take one's seat</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to sit</i> as suppliants, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to sit down in a country, encamp</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}